{"tid":1052070,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實除左三八婦女節，仲有國際男士節","createTime":"2019-03-08T05:05:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-08T06:41:06.000Z","uid":67454,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b0b4d9e80d41ffbecd80744d9954d686b51d86cb","tid":1052070,"uid":67454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T05:05:01.000Z","msg":"國際男人節（英文：International Men's Day，簡稱IMD）是國際上每年舉行的慶祝男性作出的貢獻的紀念日，通常設立在11月19日。該活動由托馬斯&middot;奧斯特於1992年2月7日創辦，並於1999年在特立尼達和多巴哥重啟。馬耳他是慶祝國際男人節最久的國家，自從1994年2月7日來從未間斷。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然成日比人忽略，但大家唔好唔記得係有男士節，如果咁都唔在乎就唔好怪女權撚當道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2aa5e1068ff9d53bc8f6c294d438dc1a81c7e0a","tid":1052070,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T05:09:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bc55d34b9245eecca8ccc957519c6503f5056d0a","tid":1052070,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T05:12:42.000Z","msg":"男士節要送戒指比心儀女性"},{"pid":"22effa2fefde96c933428754d79aa4fc40c6fc67","tid":1052070,"uid":15348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T05:13:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a0ff00c2a5cea4cf67396992cbaa9fb90571920","tid":1052070,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2aa5e1068ff9d53bc8f6c294d438dc1a81c7e0a","tid":1052070,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T05:09:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T05:17:37.000Z","msg":"肥絲大隻節<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fdd705f7311ecd9a59d4d2c8cb149f1d20562ed","tid":1052070,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T05:19:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7456970404a773b9a0dd60c296d80de438c7b36b","tid":1052070,"uid":67454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T05:21:34.000Z",